testcase.name: Empty: center of mass should be the center of the cell
Fork with 3 empty quadrants and 1 leaf (nw)
Empty.insert(b) should return a Leaf with only that body
Body.updated should do nothing for Empty quad trees
Body.updated should take bodies in a Leaf into account
'SectorMatrix.+=' should add a body at (25,47) to the correct bucket of a sector matrix of size 96
